---
title: Zesty Honey-Lemon Chicken with Savoury Rice and Zucchini
description: Highlighting the tasty pairing of honey and lemon, this comforting chicken dish hits all the right notes without a fussy technique to bog you down. The holy trinity of onions, celery and carrots lend their savouriness to the rice and tones down the sweet tartness of the sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-miel-et-citron-178f844a.jpg
